(211, 'Ambulance progress ''not fast enough''', 'The ambulance service in Wales is not improving quickly enough, a cross-party committee of AMs warns.', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-32147576#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
(212, 'Care system gets ''biggest shake-up''', 'Major changes to the care system in England, dubbed the biggest shake-up for 60 years, are being introduced, while Scotland merges NHS and care budgets.', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-32136209#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
(213, 'Paracetamol ‘no good for back pain''', 'Paracetamol is ineffective at treating back pain and osteoarthritis despite being a recommended treatment, a group of Australian researchers warns.', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-32132377#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
(214, 'MS drug ''may already be out there''', 'Depression and heart disease drugs are to be tested in a new trial to find treatments for Multiple Sclerosis (MS).', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-32136208#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
(215, 'More veterans seek mental health aid', 'A mental health charity which treats military veterans says referrals have increased by 26% in the last year.', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-32126052#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
(216, 'Medieval eye remedy ''kills MRSA''', 'A 1,000-year-old treatment for eye infections could hold the key to killing antibiotic-resistant superbugs, scientists say.', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-nottinghamshire-32117815#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
(217, 'DNA of ''an entire nation'' assessed', 'The genetic code of "an entire nation" has effectively been deduced, say researchers in Iceland.', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-32024158#sa-ns_mchannel=rss&ns_source=PublicRSS20-sa', 12),
